 "remarks": "Turn-key, move in ready modern townhouse located in the heart of downtown New Canaan, this home offers three floors of elegant living with the feel of a single-family residence and the convenience of low-maintenance living. The renovated open floor plan features a state of the art newer chef&apos;s kitchen, a breakfast nook, island, and a light-filled living room/dining room with a fireplace. The main floor offers a study or additional bedroom with its own fireplace and large windows. On the second floor, you will find the owner suite featuring- a renovated luxury bathroom with soaking tub, shower, 2 vanities, two walk-in fitted closets-along with two additional bedrooms, a full bath, and a laundry area. The lower level provides nearly 1,000 square feet of additional walk out living space with fireplace large recreation room and a patio. Outside, the walk-out lower level leads to a private patio and yard, offering a quiet oasis which backs up to a Bristow Park Bird Sanctuary and Mead Park. A short stroll on sidewalks to Metro North train station, shops, restaurants and the beautiful village of New Canaan.",
